/>\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線：改唔到<br />\n<br />\n會唔會快天黑：<br />\n唔會，因為我地行既路線係由東向西 都係對住個太陽，而且周遭無大廈擋光<br />\n唔似港島咁所以唔會咁快變暗<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無轉述有錯 詳情可TG @maxchung 查詢"},{"pid":"c8f898bf4a19832237e96a0502151a289566fce9","tid":1358140,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"最終時間同路線跟警方ok嗰個就算，之後就要因應嗰個方案制定大方向策略<br />\n<br />\n到時夠料會考慮開post<br />\n<br />\n利申: 和理非，ex住元朗所以ok熟市中心(雖然已經好耐)但到時臨場策略交由現場決定，因為有事到時嚟唔到，只可以略盡棉力<br />\n<br />\n今次建議巴打或有市中心居民預先踩場了解路線同環境，this time 係唔講得笑"},{"pid":"3df177eae5e6534057d8cfba55acde45d290ac7c","tid":1358140,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"你地入左公海gp未<br />\n我暫時唔得閒Pm你地住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d86cf91233f8304f487f85c1147849500d2b7ec","tid":1358140,"uid":208492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd103c4ae65c4af1e9397d8db7ed5e21fb56d7bc","tid":1358140,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"雞地太近村"},{"pid":"a80113e94696bba96c5487b597adb2d03dd8235d","tid":1358140,"uid":37577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"樓主唔得閒代Po：<br />\n而家727不反對通知書會係3點開始，同鐘生交流過就係因為唔想時間太早比狗太早封站所以簡3點開始<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482fdfc22f8d2d659bc7d12a23d314c8aa423b0e","tid":1358140,"uid":37577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}